<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,342,1080,1106]" pageId="9" pageNumber="10">Distribution</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="9.[189,660,1134,1160]" box="[189,660,1134,1160]" pageId="9" pageNumber="10">Europe. Not yet in the Nordic countries.</paragraph>
